    <summary>Easier cron triggering for your Magento store. SimpleCron eliminates the need to configure a separate scheduled task and periodically triggers your store's cron jobs automatically!</summary>
    <description>SimpleCron simplifies an important part of any Magento setup, the cron job. Especially useful for stores that don't have a way to create crontab entries, this simple Magento cron extension will periodically (at an interval you choose) trigger your store's cron jobs. Install it and forget it; you'll never need to worry about your crontab or scheduled task failing again.</description>
